<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Climate Solutions</title>
  <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/' }) %>

  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="hero bg-base-200 my-6 p-6 rounded-lg">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Explore Climate Solutions Projects</h1>
          <p class="py-6">Discover innovative ways to reduce carbon emissions and help our planet thrive.</p>
          <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Projects</a>
          <p class="mt-4">Harman Singh - 121451231</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/alternativeCement.jpg" alt="Alternative Cement">
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement <span class="text-sm font-light">(Industry)</span></h2>
          <p>New cement formulas can drastically reduce CO2 emissions in construction.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-outline">View Project</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/bicycle.avif" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure">
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure <span class="text-sm font-light">(Transportation)</span></h2>
          <p>Building more bike lanes to promote eco-friendly commuting and reduce traffic emissions.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-outline">View Project</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/landRestoration.avif" alt="Tree Restoration">
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Tree Restoration <span class="text-sm font-light">(Land Sinks)</span></h2>
          <p>Large-scale tree planting and forest restoration to increase carbon absorption capacity.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-outline">View Project</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>